{"tid":2242372,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"The United Nations Commission on Human Lefts","createTime":"2020-10-14T03:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T14:39:23.000Z","uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2231373021d9c76da851e4189535cbe446a34e82","tid":2242372,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18efd0c0ca4985c9d691a9802ba6fbeb505249ec","tid":2242372,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc51aa6258997b853cf903001aafb73d4ec82d12","tid":2242372,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad86c3c5b5f426449603089a8a0ef1e4b03eeeeb","tid":2242372,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc51aa6258997b853cf903001aafb73d4ec82d12","tid":2242372,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n最近沙皮狗經常違反板規證據:<br />\n沙皮狗請回應 有冇報章轉載權； 請LIHKG嚴肅跟進#133680侵犯版權問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194433</a><br />\n<br />\n擁有分身證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"2517c2fc12694499d8bb936bd78d68cb8cc75781","tid":2242372,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18efd0c0ca4985c9d691a9802ba6fbeb505249ec","tid":2242372,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"Lefts可以包晒左膠同極端左狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf51912ebc2a9702584f97c4b26eed7a57b0209","tid":2242372,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fc51aa6258997b853cf903001aafb73d4ec82d12","tid":2242372,"uid":133680,"like":